{"id": 1473, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近你有哪些“一夜回到解放前”的感觉？", "description": "曾经把大家都宠坏了的各种互联网服务都变得不靠谱了。（题图来自：Golden Cosmos）", "record_count": 7077, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170124131249WbQzI5DUFGiuLh4T.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-25T03:00:30Z", "options": [{"id": 158720, "content": "需要花钱的东西越来越多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916783}, {"id": 165376, "content": "背过的书，过个年，忘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932926}, {"id": 158209, "content": "金融危机，一辈子努力化为泡影", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896452}, {"id": 158465, "content": "鬼怪看完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902329}, {"id": 159489, "content": "熊孩子来我家，看到了我还没来得及关上的电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715685}, {"id": 162049, "content": "各种断签", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92975}, {"id": 158210, "content": "高数吃的不透，觉得数学一夜回到解放前", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759799}, {"id": 158466, "content": "现在都是啥吋候了？快过年了，让我们高高兴兴的过年吧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901976}, {"id": 158211, "content": "停电", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882780}, {"id": 158467, "content": "还完房贷后的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768619}, {"id": 160003, "content": "五天上黄金，一天回青铜﻿(▼皿▼#)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920239}, {"id": 158212, "content": "很有成就感的打完一个特别靠运气的副本，然后结算错误", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912703}, {"id": 158468, "content": "春节各种餐馆都关门了…外卖好多也停了…没有东西吃……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130994}, {"id": 158724, "content": "小学生出没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173539}, {"id": 162308, "content": "读书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895728}, {"id": 158213, "content": "高数考完", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436707}, {"id": 158469, "content": "春节了，客户不给结款。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805966}, {"id": 160005, "content": "压岁钱莫名其妙的就花完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920241}, {"id": 160773, "content": "游戏不小心删档了，(T＿T)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922161}, {"id": 158214, "content": "快递就是不到货", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913330}, {"id": 158470, "content": "买票，回家比二十年前还难\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 173062, "content": "百度网盘开始限速了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953835}, {"id": 158215, "content": "快播没了，百度云也没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836324}, {"id": 158471, "content": "什么？我大清亡了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761842}, {"id": 158216, "content": "还没拿到工资就已经没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870354}, {"id": 158472, "content": "上缴了工资卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513214}, {"id": 160008, "content": "每天一睁眼看到手机提示  距离高考还有492天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184381}, {"id": 168456, "content": "韩剧看完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061245}, {"id": 158217, "content": "辛苦了一年，存款0。受气又受累π_π", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72816}, {"id": 158218, "content": "放寒假了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654211}, {"id": 158474, "content": "交完房租发现这个月没有了收入?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916053}, {"id": 161290, "content": "规律的生物钟，一放假又全乱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923528}, {"id": 158219, "content": "重装电脑系统，网卡不匹配了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914355}, {"id": 158475, "content": "广西鹿寨化肥有限责任公司和广西区投资公司的黑心领导一脚把鹿化公司2000多职工全部踹出！奉献了大半辈子的工厂全体职工被迫下岗！工作没了身体垮了再求职超龄了！?????????", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916062}, {"id": 158220, "content": "减了一个暑假的肥，寒假过年养起来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914355}, {"id": 158476, "content": "电脑彻底坏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916074}, {"id": 159756, "content": "没网络了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539385}, {"id": 158222, "content": "特朗普不解释", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907091}, {"id": 169742, "content": "凸凸凸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937851}, {"id": 158223, "content": "网络有很多游戏不能直播了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895042}, {"id": 168719, "content": "体重", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 158224, "content": "发年终奖的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833468}, {"id": 158736, "content": "要过年了，结果却生病了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916820}, {"id": 160017, "content": "三观崩坏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781562}, {"id": 158738, "content": "初九就得开学……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636272}, {"id": 162322, "content": "啊？我就吃了桶泡面啊。偶尔改变下生活嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926182}, {"id": 158227, "content": "快递用买个邮票吗！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576828}, {"id": 158483, "content": "想买椰子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886467}, {"id": 160531, "content": "回乡下老家没网络！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579390}, {"id": 158228, "content": "木有年终奖……?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915457}]}